layout.p:
Columns: 153;
                                                  ruled lines: 63;
                                                  written lines: 63; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point.Visible pricking and stiching. 153 columns in total, three to six columns per membrane. Occasional tagin on שעטנזגץ (except at the beginning of Numbers). Majuscular and minuscular letter in accordance with the rules. Special shapes of the letter ז, נ, פ and broken ו occur infrequently. The "puncta extraordinaria" placed on the words fixed by masorah (with a few exceptions). Several lines and parts of lines written on erasures.
